## ğŸš€ How to Use
1. Clone or download this repository.  
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.  
3. Modify `style.css` to experiment with different flexbox properties.

## ğŸ“š Key Flexbox Properties Used
- `display: flex;` â€“ Enables Flexbox layout  
- `justify-content` â€“ Controls horizontal alignment  
- `align-items` â€“ Controls vertical alignment  
- `flex-wrap` â€“ Allows items to wrap onto multiple lines  
- `flex-grow`, `flex-shrink`, `flex-basis` â€“ Controls item size behavior  

